                "caption": "Figure 2:Pointwise metrics only weakly capture local surface geometry.We add low- and high-frequency perturbations to the same ground-truth point map.AbsRelglob\\text{AbsRel}_{\\text{glob}}andAbsRelloc\\text{AbsRel}_{\\text{loc}}average pointwise position errors, giving nearly identical scores even though the high-frequency perturbation yields much less coherent local surface geometry.MAEnormal\\text{MAE}_{\\text{normal}}instead compares point map normals induced by neighboring point differences, and therefore reflects this degradation.",
